專業英語課程 (ESP)
首頁課程資料專業英文課程(ESP)跨文化議題-歐洲各國文化選讀





 


 


跨文化議題-歐洲各國文化選讀


教學目標




1.
To provide an instruction in accordance with the principles of ESP teaching;


2.
To provide students with various input promoting knowledge and understanding of chosen aspects of European culture;


3.
To familiarize learners with selected culture texts, such as literary texts, movies, songs, and painting;


4.
To promote development of reading, writing, speaking, and listening in English;


5.
To support learners’ autonomy and encourage them to use additional sources of information;


6.
To inspire a long-term interest in the target topic.


 
 




